race.comment: HELLO MARY (2) has switched from a Victoria stable and she was last seen 33 days ago winning a 56 at Kilmore. Her form overall reads well for this and expect her to take beating. SUPER SHARP (1) was quickly back on track, leading and placing this grade/trip. Keeps a handy 2kg claim and will give a big sight again. THE BIG FREEZE (3) was quickly back on track 6 days ago easily winning a 58 from the speed. Will carry just 53kg this grade with the 3kg claim atop and that brings him into it. VALLEY PRINCE (4) tries hard and with the weight relief can fill a slot if he puts his best foot forward. Top three contender.
